<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='300000' id='t-300000'>We turn every moment of every day</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='302000' id='t-302000'>into a race to the finish line --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='304000' id='t-304000'>a finish line, incidentally, that we never reach,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='307000' id='t-307000'>but a finish line nonetheless.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='309000' id='t-309000'>And I guess that the question is,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='311000' id='t-311000'>is it possible to break free from that mindset?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='313000' id='t-313000'>And thankfully, the answer is yes, because</span>
