<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='323000' id='t-323000'>Right across the world, people are doing the unthinkable:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='326000' id='t-326000'>they're slowing down, and finding that,</span>
